{"word":"Sihor","slug":"sihor","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sihor</b> <a href=\"#/H7883\">H7883</a> <br/> Called also Shihor, a river of Egypt, given by some authorities as the Nile.<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=3'>Jos 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=13&verse=5'>1Ch 13:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=23&verse=3'>Isa 23:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=18'>Jer 2:18</a>"}]}